{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_10_01_short",
  "title": "川咲さくら 1話 味わってあげたいんです！ (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、{user}さん！\n一件目のお仕事終わって、帰ってきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work‚ {user}-san!\nI finished today's first job and came back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おかえり、さくら\nすまないな、今日も同行出来なくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Welcome back‚ Sakura.\nSorry I couldn't accompany you today either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえ！　しょうがないですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not at all! It can't be helped.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.2269387245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "私達、BIG4入りして以来ずっと忙しいですし\nそれに今や、月ストにリズノワだってBIG4",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've been busy ever since we joined BIG4.\nAnd now‚ Moon Tempest and LizNoir are also BIG4.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.1333330154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが忙しくなるのも\n嬉しい悲鳴かもですね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san getting busy\nmight be a happy problem!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "はは、さくらは相変わらず前向きだな\nでもその通りだ。今が踏ん張りどころの正念場だぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ Sakura is as positive as always.\nBut that's right. Now is the crucial time to persevere.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.2666671116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "沢山呼んでもらえるうちに、どれだけ自分達の価値を\n示せるかどうかで、今後の仕事の入り方が変わるからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "While we're being called upon a lot‚ how much we can\nshow our worth will change how we get work in the future.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.800000445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　大変だなって思う時も少しはありますけど\n月ストやリズノワにも負けてられないですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! There are times when I think it's tough‚ but\nwe can't lose to Moon Tempest or LizNoir either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.7333337783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "これからも明るく楽しく、出来る仕事をコツコツと\n積み重ねられるよう、頑張ります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll keep going with positivity and joy‚\nsteadily building up the work I can do!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.3666671116,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9200.000063599993,
          "startTime": 67.5666671752
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "とはいえ、体調管理にも気をつけないとな\n意識してオフは差し込むようにしてるけど……ん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That said‚ you need to be careful about your health too.\nI try to make sure to fit in some breaks‚ but… hmm?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.1666671116,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
